        <mj-text font-family="'Trebuchet MS', Trebuchet, 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif" font-size="20px" font-family="'Trebuchet MS', Trebuchet, 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif" color="#000">A new beginning</mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#3B3B3B">Hello everyone,<br><br>you may have already noticed, that the newsletters design and sender have changed. The change doesn't stop there! I have entirely rebuild the website from the ground up and published it on a new url.<br><br>Why? Simply put: The old system was too complicated to publish articles, send pictures and adapt to my needs. On the new website for example, I have made language switching easier and there is a gallery to showcase (nearly) all my pictures, so you can get a nice overview of Peru and this incredible year.<br><br>I moved all the e-mail addresses to this new system as well as all the articles, which I edited. The site is in constant development, thus being subject to change with new functions i deem nice or neccessary.<br><br>Happy reading to everyone,<br>buenos días y hasta la proxíma! </mj-text>
